Class ComponentLibrary

  • java.lang.Object
    • nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.gp20.application.ComponentLibrary

  • public class ComponentLibrary
extends java.lang.Object
    A class used for storing and retrieving fonts, colours and icon images. Follows the Singleton design pattern https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Singleton_pattern
